00915 static int
00916 PairInTables(
00917   DdNode * g,
00918   DdNode * h,
00919   st_table * ghTable)
00920 {
00921     int valueG, valueH, gPresent, hPresent;
00922 
00923     valueG = valueH = gPresent = hPresent = 0;
00924     
00925     gPresent = st_lookup_int(ghTable, (char *)Cudd_Regular(g), &valueG);
00926     hPresent = st_lookup_int(ghTable, (char *)Cudd_Regular(h), &valueH);
00927 
00928     if (!gPresent && !hPresent) return(NONE);
00929 
00930     if (!hPresent) {
00931         if (valueG & 1) return(G_ST);
00932         if (valueG & 2) return(G_CR);
00933     }
00934     if (!gPresent) {
00935         if (valueH & 1) return(H_CR);
00936         if (valueH & 2) return(H_ST);
00937     }
00938     /* both in tables */
00939     if ((valueG & 1) && (valueH & 2)) return(PAIR_ST);
00940     if ((valueG & 2) && (valueH & 1)) return(PAIR_CR);
00941     
00942     if (valueG & 1) {
00943         return(BOTH_G);
00944     } else {
00945         return(BOTH_H);
00946     }
00947     
00948 } /* end of PairInTables */

00991             } else {

00997                 return(NULL);
00998             }
00999         }
01000         factors->g = g;
01001         factors->h = h;
01002     } else  if ((pairValue == BOTH_G) || (pairValue == G_ST)) {
01003         if (h != one) {
01004             value = 0;
01005             if (st_lookup_int(ghTable, (char *)Cudd_Regular(h), &value)) {
01006                 value |= 2;
01007             } else {
01008                 value = 2;

01010             if (st_insert(ghTable, (char *)Cudd_Regular(h),
01011                           (char *)(long)value) == ST_OUT_OF_MEM) {
01012                 (void) fprintf(stderr, "Out of memory\n");
01013                 return(NULL);
01014             }
01015         }
01016         factors->g = g;
01017         factors->h = h;
01018     } else if (pairValue == H_CR) {
01019         if (g != one) {
01020             value = 2;
01021             if (st_insert(ghTable, (char *)Cudd_Regular(g),

01074 static Conjuncts *
01075 PickOnePair(
01076   DdNode * node,
01077   DdNode * g1,
01078   DdNode * h1,
01079   DdNode * g2,
01080   DdNode * h2,
01081   st_table * ghTable,
01082   st_table * cacheTable)
01083 {
01084     int value;
01085     Conjuncts *factors;
01086     int oneRef, twoRef;
01087     
01088     factors = ALLOC(Conjuncts, 1);
01089     if (factors == NULL) return(NULL);
01090 
01091     /* count the number of pointers to pair 2 */
01092     if (h2 == one) {
01093         twoRef = (Cudd_Regular(g2))->ref;
01094     } else if (g2 == one) {
01095         twoRef = (Cudd_Regular(h2))->ref;
01096     } else {
01097         twoRef = ((Cudd_Regular(g2))->ref + (Cudd_Regular(h2))->ref)/2;
01098     }
01099 
01100     /* count the number of pointers to pair 1 */
01101     if (h1 == one) {
01102         oneRef  = (Cudd_Regular(g1))->ref;
01103     } else if (g1 == one) {
01104         oneRef  = (Cudd_Regular(h1))->ref;
01105     } else {
01106         oneRef = ((Cudd_Regular(g1))->ref + (Cudd_Regular(h1))->ref)/2;
01107     }
01108 
01109     /* pick the pair with higher reference count */
01110     if (oneRef >= twoRef) {
01111         factors->g = g1;
01112         factors->h = h1;
01113     } else {
01114         factors->g = g2;
01115         factors->h = h2;
01116     }
01117     
01118     /*
01119      * Store computed factors in respective tables to encourage
01120      * recombination.
01121      */
01122     if (factors->g != one) {
01123         /* insert g in htable */
01124         value = 0;
01125         if (st_lookup_int(ghTable, (char *)Cudd_Regular(factors->g), &value)) {
01126             if (value == 2) {
01127                 value |= 1;
01128                 if (st_insert(ghTable, (char *)Cudd_Regular(factors->g),
01129                               (char *)(long)value) == ST_OUT_OF_MEM) {
01130                     (void) fprintf(stderr, "Out of memory\n");
01131                     FREE(factors);
01132                     return(NULL);
01133                 }
01134             }
01135         } else {
01136             value = 1;
01137             if (st_insert(ghTable, (char *)Cudd_Regular(factors->g),
01138                           (char *)(long)value) == ST_OUT_OF_MEM) {
01139                 (void) fprintf(stderr, "Out of memory\n");
01140                 FREE(factors);
01141                 return(NULL);
01142             }
01143         }
01144     }
01145 
01146     if (factors->h != one) {
01147         /* insert h in htable */
01148         value = 0;
01149         if (st_lookup_int(ghTable, (char *)Cudd_Regular(factors->h), &value)) {
01150             if (value == 1) {
01151                 value |= 2;
01152                 if (st_insert(ghTable, (char *)Cudd_Regular(factors->h),
01153                               (char *)(long)value) == ST_OUT_OF_MEM) {
01154                     (void) fprintf(stderr, "Out of memory\n");
01155                     FREE(factors);
01156                     return(NULL);
01157                 }
01158             }       
01159         } else {
01160             value = 2;
01161             if (st_insert(ghTable, (char *)Cudd_Regular(factors->h),
01162                           (char *)(long)value) == ST_OUT_OF_MEM) {
01163                 (void) fprintf(stderr, "Out of memory\n");
01164                 FREE(factors);
01165                 return(NULL);
01166             }
01167         }
01168     }
01169     
01170     /* Store factors in cache table for later use. */
01171     if (st_insert(cacheTable, (char *)node, (char *)factors) ==
01172             ST_OUT_OF_MEM) {
01173         (void) fprintf(stderr, "Out of memory\n");
01174         FREE(factors);
01175         return(NULL);
01176     }
01177 
01178     return(factors);
01179 
01180 } /* end of PickOnePair */

01478             dd->errorCode = CUDD_MEMORY_OUT;

01485         /* store  x in g table, the other node is already in the table */
01486         if (st_lookup_int(ghTable, (char *)Cudd_Regular(x), &value)) {
01487             value |= 1;
01488         } else {
01489             value = 1;
01490         }
01491         if (st_insert(ghTable, (char *)Cudd_Regular(x), (char *)(long)value) == ST_OUT_OF_MEM) {
01492             fprintf(stdout, "gTable insert failed\n");

01548             return NULL;

01552          */
01553         factors = CheckTablesCacheAndReturn(node,
01554                                             g,
01555                                             h,
01556                                             ghTable,
01557                                             cacheTable);
01558         if (factors == NULL) {
01559             dd->errorCode = CUDD_MEMORY_OUT;
01560             Cudd_RecursiveDeref(dd, g);
01561             Cudd_RecursiveDeref(dd, h);

01568     Hnv = cuddE(H);
01569     Hv = Cudd_NotCond(Hv, Cudd_IsComplement(node));
01570     Hnv = Cudd_NotCond(Hnv, Cudd_IsComplement(node));
01571     /* if the child below is a variable */
01572     if ((Hv == zero) || (Hnv == zero)) {
01573         g = factorsNv->g;
01574         h = cuddBddAndRecur(dd, x, factorsNv->h);
01575         if (h!= NULL) cuddRef(h);
01576         Cudd_RecursiveDeref(dd, factorsNv->h);
01577         Cudd_RecursiveDeref(dd, x);
01578         if (h == NULL) {
01579             Cudd_RecursiveDeref(dd, factorsNv->g);
01580             return NULL;
01581         }
01582         /* CheckTablesCacheAndReturn responsible for allocating
01583          * factors structure.g,h referenced for table store 
01584          */
01585         factors = CheckTablesCacheAndReturn(node,
01586                                             g,
01587                                             h,
01588                                             ghTable,
01589                                             cacheTable);
01590         if (factors == NULL) {
01591             dd->errorCode = CUDD_MEMORY_OUT;
01592             Cudd_RecursiveDeref(dd, g);
01593             Cudd_RecursiveDeref(dd, h);
01594         }
01595         return(factors); 
01596     }
01597 
01598     /* build g1 = x*g; h1 = h */
01599     /* build g2 = g; h2 = x*h */
01600     Cudd_RecursiveDeref(dd, x);
01601     h1 = factorsNv->h;
01602     g1 = cuddBddAndRecur(dd, x, factorsNv->g);
01603     if (g1 != NULL) cuddRef(g1);
01604     if (g1 == NULL) {
01605         Cudd_RecursiveDeref(dd, factorsNv->g); 
01606         Cudd_RecursiveDeref(dd, factorsNv->h);
01607         return NULL;
01608     }
01609     
01610     g2 = factorsNv->g;
01611     h2 = cuddBddAndRecur(dd, x, factorsNv->h);
01612     if (h2 != NULL) cuddRef(h2);
01613     if (h2 == NULL) {
01614         Cudd_RecursiveDeref(dd, factorsNv->h);
01615         Cudd_RecursiveDeref(dd, factorsNv->g);
01616         return NULL;
01617     }
01618 
01619     /* check whether any pair is in tables */
01620     factors = CheckInTables(node, g1, h1, g2, h2, ghTable, cacheTable, &outOfMem);
01621     if (outOfMem) {
01622         dd->errorCode = CUDD_MEMORY_OUT;
01623         Cudd_RecursiveDeref(dd, g1);
01624         Cudd_RecursiveDeref(dd, h1);
01625         Cudd_RecursiveDeref(dd, g2);
01626         Cudd_RecursiveDeref(dd, h2);
01627         return NULL;
01628     }
01629     if (factors != NULL) {
01630         if ((factors->g == g1) || (factors->g == h1)) {
01631             Cudd_RecursiveDeref(dd, g2);
01632             Cudd_RecursiveDeref(dd, h2);
01633         } else {
01634             Cudd_RecursiveDeref(dd, g1);
01635             Cudd_RecursiveDeref(dd, h1);
01636         }
01637         return factors;
01638     }
01639 
01640     /* check for each pair in tables and choose one */
01641     factors = PickOnePair(node,g1, h1, g2, h2, ghTable, cacheTable);
01642     if (factors == NULL) {
01643         dd->errorCode = CUDD_MEMORY_OUT;
01644         Cudd_RecursiveDeref(dd, g1);
01645         Cudd_RecursiveDeref(dd, h1);
01646         Cudd_RecursiveDeref(dd, g2);
01647         Cudd_RecursiveDeref(dd, h2);
01648     } else {
01649         /* now free what was created and not used */
01650         if ((factors->g == g1) || (factors->g == h1)) {
01651             Cudd_RecursiveDeref(dd, g2);
01652             Cudd_RecursiveDeref(dd, h2);
01653         } else {
01654             Cudd_RecursiveDeref(dd, g1);
01655             Cudd_RecursiveDeref(dd, h1);
01656         }
01657     }
01658         
01659     return(factors);
01660 } /* end of ZeroCase */

01662 
01682 static Conjuncts *
01683 BuildConjuncts(
01684   DdManager * dd,
01685   DdNode * node,
01686   st_table * distanceTable,
01687   st_table * cacheTable,
01688   int approxDistance,
01689   int maxLocalRef,
01690   st_table * ghTable,
01691   st_table * mintermTable)
01692 {
01693     int topid, distance;
01694     Conjuncts *factorsNv = NULL, *factorsNnv = NULL, *factors;
01695     Conjuncts *dummy;
01696     DdNode *N, *Nv, *Nnv, *temp, *g1, *g2, *h1, *h2, *topv;
01697     double minNv = 0.0, minNnv = 0.0;
01698     double *doubleDummy;
01699     int switched =0;
01700     int outOfMem;
01701     int freeNv = 0, freeNnv = 0, freeTemp;
01702     NodeStat *nodeStat;
01703     int value;
01704 
01705     /* if f is constant, return (f,f) */
01706     if (Cudd_IsConstant(node)) {
01707         factors = ALLOC(Conjuncts, 1);
01708         if (factors == NULL) {
01709             dd->errorCode = CUDD_MEMORY_OUT;
01710             return(NULL);
01711         }
01712         factors->g = node;
01713         factors->h = node;
01714         return(FactorsComplement(factors));
01715     }
01716 
01717     /* If result (a pair of conjuncts) in cache, return the factors. */
01718     if (st_lookup(cacheTable, (char *)node, (char **)&dummy)) {
01719         factors = dummy;
01720         return(factors);
01721     }
01722     
01723     /* check distance and local reference count of this node */
01724     N = Cudd_Regular(node);
01725     if (!st_lookup(distanceTable, (char *)N, (char **)&nodeStat)) {
01726         (void) fprintf(stdout, "Not in table, Something wrong\n");
01727         return(NULL);
01728     }
01729     distance = nodeStat->distance;
01730 
01731     /* at or below decomposition point, return (f, 1) */
01732     if (((nodeStat->localRef > maxLocalRef*2/3) &&
01733          (distance < approxDistance*2/3)) ||
01734             (distance <= approxDistance/4)) {
01735         factors = ALLOC(Conjuncts, 1);
01736         if (factors == NULL) {
01737             dd->errorCode = CUDD_MEMORY_OUT;
01738             return(NULL);
01739         }
01740         /* alternate assigning (f,1) */
01741         value = 0;
01742         if (st_lookup_int(ghTable, (char *)Cudd_Regular(node), &value)) {
01743             if (value == 3) {
01744                 if (!lastTimeG) {
01745                     factors->g = node;
01746                     factors->h = one;
01747                     lastTimeG = 1;
01748                 } else {
01749                     factors->g = one;
01750                     factors->h = node;
01751                     lastTimeG = 0; 
01752                 }
01753             } else if (value == 1) {
01754                 factors->g = node;
01755                 factors->h = one;
01756             } else {
01757                 factors->g = one;
01758                 factors->h = node;
01759             }
01760         } else if (!lastTimeG) {
01761             factors->g = node;
01762             factors->h = one;
01763             lastTimeG = 1;
01764             value = 1;
01765             if (st_insert(ghTable, (char *)Cudd_Regular(node), (char *)(long)value) == ST_OUT_OF_MEM) {
01766                 fprintf(stdout, "gTable insert failed\n");
01767                 dd->errorCode = CUDD_MEMORY_OUT;
01768                 FREE(factors);
01769                 return NULL;
01770             }
01771         } else {
01772             factors->g = one;
01773             factors->h = node;
01774             lastTimeG = 0;
01775             value = 2;
01776             if (st_insert(ghTable, (char *)Cudd_Regular(node), (char *)(long)value) == ST_OUT_OF_MEM) {
01777                 fprintf(stdout, "gTable insert failed\n");
01778                 dd->errorCode = CUDD_MEMORY_OUT;
01779                 FREE(factors);
01780                 return NULL;
01781             }
01782         }
01783         return(FactorsComplement(factors));
01784     }
01785     
01786     /* get the children and recur */
01787     Nv = cuddT(N);
01788     Nnv = cuddE(N);
01789     Nv = Cudd_NotCond(Nv, Cudd_IsComplement(node));
01790     Nnv = Cudd_NotCond(Nnv, Cudd_IsComplement(node));
01791 
01792     /* Choose which subproblem to solve first based on the number of
01793      * minterms. We go first where there are more minterms.
01794      */
01795     if (!Cudd_IsConstant(Nv)) {
01796         if (!st_lookup(mintermTable, (char *)Nv, (char **)&doubleDummy)) {
01797             (void) fprintf(stdout, "Not in table: Something wrong\n");
01798             return(NULL);
01799         }
01800         minNv = *doubleDummy;
01801     }
01802     
01803     if (!Cudd_IsConstant(Nnv)) {
01804         if (!st_lookup(mintermTable, (char *)Nnv, (char **)&doubleDummy)) {
01805             (void) fprintf(stdout, "Not in table: Something wrong\n");
01806             return(NULL);
01807         }
01808         minNnv = *doubleDummy;
01809     }
01810     
01811     if (minNv < minNnv) {
01812         temp = Nv;
01813         Nv = Nnv;
01814         Nnv = temp;
01815         switched = 1;
01816     }
01817 
01818     /* build gt, ht recursively */
01819     if (Nv != zero) {
01820         factorsNv = BuildConjuncts(dd, Nv, distanceTable,
01821                                    cacheTable, approxDistance, maxLocalRef, 
01822                                    ghTable, mintermTable);
01823         if (factorsNv == NULL) return(NULL);
01824         freeNv = FactorsNotStored(factorsNv);
01825         factorsNv = (freeNv) ? FactorsUncomplement(factorsNv) : factorsNv;
01826         cuddRef(factorsNv->g);
01827         cuddRef(factorsNv->h);
01828         
01829         /* Deal with the zero case */
01830         if (Nnv == zero) {
01831             /* is responsible for freeing factorsNv */
01832             factors = ZeroCase(dd, node, factorsNv, ghTable,
01833                                cacheTable, switched);
01834             if (freeNv) FREE(factorsNv);
01835             return(factors);
01836         }
01837     }
01838 
01839     /* build ge, he recursively */
01840     if (Nnv != zero) {
01841         factorsNnv = BuildConjuncts(dd, Nnv, distanceTable,
01842                                     cacheTable, approxDistance, maxLocalRef,
01843                                     ghTable, mintermTable);
01844         if (factorsNnv == NULL) {
01845             Cudd_RecursiveDeref(dd, factorsNv->g);
01846             Cudd_RecursiveDeref(dd, factorsNv->h);
01847             if (freeNv) FREE(factorsNv);
01848             return(NULL);
01849         }
01850         freeNnv = FactorsNotStored(factorsNnv);
01851         factorsNnv = (freeNnv) ? FactorsUncomplement(factorsNnv) : factorsNnv;
01852         cuddRef(factorsNnv->g);
01853         cuddRef(factorsNnv->h);
01854         
01855         /* Deal with the zero case */
01856         if (Nv == zero) {
01857             /* is responsible for freeing factorsNv */
01858             factors = ZeroCase(dd, node, factorsNnv, ghTable,
01859                                cacheTable, switched);
01860             if (freeNnv) FREE(factorsNnv);
01861             return(factors);
01862         }
01863     }
01864 
01865     /* construct the 2 pairs */
01866     /* g1 = x*gt + x'*ge; h1 = x*ht + x'*he; */
01867     /* g2 = x*gt + x'*he; h2 = x*ht + x'*ge */
01868     if (switched) {
01869         factors = factorsNnv;
01870         factorsNnv = factorsNv;
01871         factorsNv = factors;
01872         freeTemp = freeNv;
01873         freeNv = freeNnv;
01874         freeNnv = freeTemp;
01875     }
01876 
01877     /* Build the factors for this node. */
01878     topid = N->index;
01879     topv = dd->vars[topid];
01880     
01881     g1 = cuddBddIteRecur(dd, topv, factorsNv->g, factorsNnv->g);
01882     if (g1 == NULL) {
01883         Cudd_RecursiveDeref(dd, factorsNv->g);
01884         Cudd_RecursiveDeref(dd, factorsNv->h);
01885         Cudd_RecursiveDeref(dd, factorsNnv->g);
01886         Cudd_RecursiveDeref(dd, factorsNnv->h);
01887         if (freeNv) FREE(factorsNv);
01888         if (freeNnv) FREE(factorsNnv);
01889         return(NULL);
01890     }
01891 
01892     cuddRef(g1);
01893 
01894     h1 = cuddBddIteRecur(dd, topv, factorsNv->h, factorsNnv->h);
01895     if (h1 == NULL) {
01896         Cudd_RecursiveDeref(dd, factorsNv->g);
01897         Cudd_RecursiveDeref(dd, factorsNv->h);
01898         Cudd_RecursiveDeref(dd, factorsNnv->g);
01899         Cudd_RecursiveDeref(dd, factorsNnv->h);
01900         Cudd_RecursiveDeref(dd, g1);
01901         if (freeNv) FREE(factorsNv);
01902         if (freeNnv) FREE(factorsNnv);
01903         return(NULL);
01904     }
01905 
01906     cuddRef(h1);
01907 
01908     g2 = cuddBddIteRecur(dd, topv, factorsNv->g, factorsNnv->h);
01909     if (g2 == NULL) {
01910         Cudd_RecursiveDeref(dd, factorsNv->h);
01911         Cudd_RecursiveDeref(dd, factorsNv->g);
01912         Cudd_RecursiveDeref(dd, factorsNnv->g);
01913         Cudd_RecursiveDeref(dd, factorsNnv->h);
01914         Cudd_RecursiveDeref(dd, g1);
01915         Cudd_RecursiveDeref(dd, h1);
01916         if (freeNv) FREE(factorsNv);
01917         if (freeNnv) FREE(factorsNnv);
01918         return(NULL);
01919     }
01920     cuddRef(g2);
01921     Cudd_RecursiveDeref(dd, factorsNv->g);
01922     Cudd_RecursiveDeref(dd, factorsNnv->h);
01923 
01924     h2 = cuddBddIteRecur(dd, topv, factorsNv->h, factorsNnv->g);
01925     if (h2 == NULL) {
01926         Cudd_RecursiveDeref(dd, factorsNv->g);
01927         Cudd_RecursiveDeref(dd, factorsNv->h);
01928         Cudd_RecursiveDeref(dd, factorsNnv->g);
01929         Cudd_RecursiveDeref(dd, factorsNnv->h);
01930         Cudd_RecursiveDeref(dd, g1);
01931         Cudd_RecursiveDeref(dd, h1);
01932         Cudd_RecursiveDeref(dd, g2);
01933         if (freeNv) FREE(factorsNv);
01934         if (freeNnv) FREE(factorsNnv);
01935         return(NULL);
01936     }
01937     cuddRef(h2);
01938     Cudd_RecursiveDeref(dd, factorsNv->h);
01939     Cudd_RecursiveDeref(dd, factorsNnv->g);
01940     if (freeNv) FREE(factorsNv);
01941     if (freeNnv) FREE(factorsNnv);
01942 
01943     /* check for each pair in tables and choose one */
01944     factors = CheckInTables(node, g1, h1, g2, h2, ghTable, cacheTable, &outOfMem);
01945     if (outOfMem) {
01946         dd->errorCode = CUDD_MEMORY_OUT;
01947         Cudd_RecursiveDeref(dd, g1);
01948         Cudd_RecursiveDeref(dd, h1);
01949         Cudd_RecursiveDeref(dd, g2);
01950         Cudd_RecursiveDeref(dd, h2);
01951         return(NULL);
01952     }
01953     if (factors != NULL) {
01954         if ((factors->g == g1) || (factors->g == h1)) {
01955             Cudd_RecursiveDeref(dd, g2);
01956             Cudd_RecursiveDeref(dd, h2);
01957         } else {
01958             Cudd_RecursiveDeref(dd, g1);
01959             Cudd_RecursiveDeref(dd, h1);
01960         }
01961         return(factors);
01962     }
01963 
01964     /* if not in tables, pick one pair */
01965     factors = PickOnePair(node,g1, h1, g2, h2, ghTable, cacheTable);
01966     if (factors == NULL) {
01967         dd->errorCode = CUDD_MEMORY_OUT;
01968         Cudd_RecursiveDeref(dd, g1);
01969         Cudd_RecursiveDeref(dd, h1);
01970         Cudd_RecursiveDeref(dd, g2);
01971         Cudd_RecursiveDeref(dd, h2);
01972     } else {
01973         /* now free what was created and not used */
01974         if ((factors->g == g1) || (factors->g == h1)) {
01975             Cudd_RecursiveDeref(dd, g2);
01976             Cudd_RecursiveDeref(dd, h2);
01977         } else {
01978             Cudd_RecursiveDeref(dd, g1);
01979             Cudd_RecursiveDeref(dd, h1);
01980         }
01981     }
01982         
01983     return(factors);
01984     
01985 } /* end of BuildConjuncts */
